{"tid":1675198,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[分析] 和你 返工 1.0","createTime":"2019-10-25T16:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T09:28:32.000Z","uid":322508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aeffa6ee89521d43599d023595da95cc07fbd048","tid":1675198,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">今日真係好多謝各位手足參與 [<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>和你 返工</strong></span>]。</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n給大家一個小總結 (P.S 雖然我唔係搞手)。<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日唔係好多手足參與到，但呢個係成功既第一步。<br />\n<br />\n今日不足及改善建議既有以下幾點，希望可以為來近既[<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">和你 返工2.0</span></strong>] 做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">----時間----</span></strong><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不足：</span></strong><br />\n- 文宣出現過係 上午 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七點/八點</span></strong> ，所以有手足未必知道準確既時間。<br />\n- 由於<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人例遲係一個習慣</span></strong>，當去到開始時間既時候，係未及時出席活動。<br />\n- 無定明一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集合時間</strong></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出發時間</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">改善：</span></strong><br />\n- 文宣必須要<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">統一指定時間</span></strong>。<br />\n- 行動時間需要有以下幾點：<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">集合時間</span></strong> (可以預早15-20分鐘，等遲到既手足都可以有機會加入)<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">出發時間</span></strong> (睇現場人數作決定)<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">----地點----</span></strong><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不足：</span></strong><br />\n- 文宣出現既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">集合地點/出發地點</span></strong>不是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">統一性</span></strong>。<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">集合地點不明確</span></strong>，範圍太大。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">改善：</span></strong><br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣內容必須一致</span></strong>，可以令手足更能作宣傳之用。<br />\n- 集合地點同上，需要每個地方有一個<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">明確既集合點</span></strong>。<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">----路線----</span></strong><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不足：</span></strong><br />\n- 文宣上既只顯示集合地點，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無一個清晰路線</span></strong>可以比手足途中加入。<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>隊頭行得太快</strong></span>，導致有手足遲少少後就要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跑去追隊尾</span></strong> (明白大家要趕番工...)。<br />\n- 因為四個分區都有兩個地方，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只有一個開始方向</span></strong>，導致活動較為混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">改善：</span></strong><br />\n- 除各集合點外，需加上<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">清晰方向路線圖</span></strong>。<br />\n- 路線上需要加上<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個或以上集合點路線方向</span></strong>。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n最後，以上只係本人小小分析及建議，歡迎批評及討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再次多謝各手足既參與，希望快D有<br />\n[<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你 返工 2.0</span></span></strong>] 出現。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便推行動文宣。<br />\n<br />\n最新 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主線</span></span></strong> 日程表  (未能收納全部，請見諒。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoffYT9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoffYT9.png&h=fc733a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9WuML0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9WuML0.png&h=fd4f7548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xku8zjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXku8zjO.jpg&h=5e0d9619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZLoe7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZLoe7e.jpg&h=4b1cf576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBGrcTV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBGrcTV.jpg&h=d4a519e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG0fYM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG0fYM3.jpg&h=a82afeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN9ekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=b3fa6ac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1160a132